translations.name: PayPal Payflow Link
translations.title: Credit/Debit card or PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: Accept Visa, MasterCard®, American Express, Discover and PayPal payments on your site by connecting a PayPal-hosted checkout page with your own internet merchant account. Customize the page to look like the rest of your site and make sure customer transactions are secure.

translations.name: PayPal Partner Hosted with PCI Compliance
translations.title: Credit/Debit card
translations.altAdminDescription: PCI compliant payments on your site with Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Discover - without PayPal-hosted pages. Maintain full control over your customers' checkout experience by providing a credit card form that will post your customers' payment details from your site's native checkout page directly to the Gateway server.

translations.name: PayPal Payments Advanced
translations.title: Credit/Debit card or PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: Accept Visa, MasterCard®, American Express, Discover and PayPal payments securely. With this all-in-one option, customers stay on your site for the entire checkout process. It simplifies PCI compliance and opens the door to more than 100 million active PayPal customers. Requires credit approval (2-3 business days).

translations.name: PayPal Payments Standard
translations.title: PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: Add a PayPal payment button to your site to accept Visa, MasterCard®, American Express, Discover and PayPal payments securely. When your customers check out, they are redirected to PayPal to pay, then return to your site after they are finished.

translations.name: PayPal Express Checkout
translations.title: PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: Create a seamless checkout experience and increase your conversion rate by opening the door to over 100 million active PayPal customers who look for and use this fast, easy, and secure way to pay.

translations.name: PayPal Adaptive payments (legacy)
translations.title: PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: This method provides automatic transfer of payments to vendor users (the type of users enabled by the Multi-vendor module). The method may not be activated unless the module Multi-vendor is installed and enabled. To use this method, store administrator is required to have an Application ID for PayPal Adaptive Payments API.

translations.name: PayPal for Marketplaces (beta)
translations.title: PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: PayPal for Marketplaces is a comprehensive payments solution for marketplaces, crowdfunding platforms, and other environments where people buy and sell goods and services or raise money. The solution is ideal if you run a multi-party commerce platform and want a flexible, end-to-end solution for processing payments.

translations.name: PayPal for Marketplaces (beta)
translations.title: PayPal
translations.altAdminDescription: PayPal for Marketplaces - это комплексное решение по приёму платежей для торговых площадок, платформ для сбора средств под проект ("краудфандинг") и других сфер, где осуществляется продажа и покупка товаров и услуг, либо сбор средств. Данное решение идеально подойдет для платформ, осуществляющих коммерческую деятельность от лица нескольких участников, и представляет собой комплексное и гибкое решение для обработки платежей на всех этапах этой деятельности.

translations.name: emerchantpay Checkout
translations.title: emerchantpay Checkout
translations.description: emerchantpay offers a secure way to pay for your order, using Credit/Debit/Prepaid Card, e-Wallet or Vouchers.
translations.altAdminDescription: Accept Credit/Debit Cards or Alternative Payments (e-Wallet, Prepaid-Cards, Vouchers etc.) via Payment Form on emerchantpay PCI-certified servers.

translations.name: emerchantpay Direct
translations.title: emerchantpay Direct
translations.description: emerchantpay offers a secure way to pay for your order, using Credit/Debit Card
translations.altAdminDescription: Direct API - allow customers to enter their CreditCard information on your website. Note: You need PCI-DSS certificate in order to enable this payment method.

translations.name: G2A Pay
translations.adminDescription: Accept transactions via 150+ payment methods. Connect with international customers. Grow worldwide.

translations.name: Meritus Payment Solutions (“MPS”) WebHost
translations.adminDescription: Accept transactions via Meritus Payment Solutions.

translations.adminDescription: Supported countries: US, UK, France, Italy & Spain.
